			<span class="sbi-screenreader">It’s fall y’all 🍻🏈🍻 Our newest fall i</span>
									<img src="https://walkingstickbrewing.com/wp-content/plugins/instagram-feed/img/placeholder.png" alt="It’s fall y’all 🍻🏈🍻 Our newest fall installs by @brysonblackevents are here!! 

Don’t forget during the @houstontexans game we’re offering $2 Oktoberfest cans during the 1Q, $3 during 2Q, $4 during 3Q and $5 for 4Q and $25 bucket specials throughout the day!

Ask John or Jackie for more details.

Every Sunday and Monday we’re offering 25% off all to-go beers and fills.

Our newest release by @thatswhatshebrewed is a decadent German lager with a biscuit-like flavor and light floral aromas with a dry finish. Catch this on tap today!!! 

Stop by and enjoy grub by @brothersjohnmobilekitchen and we’re open until 10pm.

